What's New in 9.0.1 

== Spotlight == 
Now you can use Spotlight to find categories to quickly find in AroundMe. 

== Apple Watch support == 
Now features a completely rewritten watchOS 2 app for faster access to local venues directly from your wrist.

== iPhone 6S and 6S Plus == 
Quickly peek for venues using 3D Touch or quickly search in AroundMe by 3D Touch the app icon.
